name: Janice Of Suburbia - ResistJam Version
description:
Do you like Mario, but also like being confused?

There's only one level, but be sure that you finish it. This was made for ResistJam 2017, and was inspired by the challenge of understanding situations from different perspectives during this period of poor-communication and lack of empathy.

Art by Corinne Groble

Programming, Music, and Sound Effects by Brian Peters

All art, coding, music, and sound effects (except for the crickets recording) made in some free time between March 3 and March 11, 2017.

Sorry there's no browser version. It was too unstable to let anybody play.

The video featured here is a COMPLETE playthrough, so if you're thinking of playing, don't watch it.
